text: Fazil Fanoos (born 6 October 1997) is an Indian cricketer. He made his List A debut for Kerala in the 2017–18 Vijay Hazare Trophy on 13 February 2018. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Indian cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Kerala cricketers
